shipxb11 - a space shooter game. This is a work in progress.

To build
========

mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=RELEASE ..
make
su -c "make install"


Font from https://karenbjones.com
Most graphics from https://opengameart.org/content/spaceship-set-32x32px

